## Phase 1 — Chat mini-PRD

### Private chat
| ID | User story | Acceptance criteria |
|----|------------|---------------------|
| P-01 | As a user, I want a list of my private conversations so I can continue chats quickly. | List shows peer, last message preview, timestamp, unread badge; opens thread on tap. |
| P-02 | As a user, I want to send and receive text messages in real time. | Message appears in thread; failed sends show retry; order consistent with server timestamps. |
| P-03 | As a user, I want **delivered** and **read** indicators so I know the other person saw my message. | Receipt states match server; UI distinguishes sent / delivered / read per product copy. |
| P-04 | As a user, I want to see when the other person is typing. | Typing indicator shows within a few seconds of activity and clears when idle. |
| P-05 | As a user, I want to **reply** to a specific message. | Reply references prior message (minimum: `reply_to` id); quoted context visible in UI. |
| P-06 | As a user, I want to send **images** (and optionally short video — **stretch**). | Upload completes; preview in thread; failures surfaced. Video = stretch unless explicitly prioritized. |
| P-07 | As a user, I want **stickers** if we keep parity with legacy. | **Phase 1.1 default** unless PM explicitly pulls stickers into P1; if P1, picker + send matches legacy behavior. |
| P-08 | As a user, I want to **block** and **unblock** others. | Blocked user cannot message me; I do not see their new messages; unblock restores. |
| P-09 | As a user, I want to **delete** messages. | Policy: **delete for me** vs **delete for everyone** defined in PM + QA; server enforces. |

### Group chat
| ID | User story | Acceptance criteria |
|----|------------|---------------------|
| G-01 | As a user, I want to create and join groups, and leave when I want. | Create/join/leave flows succeed; member list updates. |
| G-02 | As a user, I want group messages with pagination and search if in scope. | History loads reliably; deep scroll does not lose position badly. |
| G-03 | As a moderator, I want **roles** (minimum: owner/admin/member — v1 may ship admin + member only). | Actions restricted by role (e.g. only admin removes members). |
| G-04 | As a user, I want **edit** and **delete** group messages per policy. | Edit/delete rules match PM + QA; audit if required. |
| G-05 | As a moderator, I want to **block a member from the group** (legacy parity). | Blocked member cannot post; unblock path exists. |

### Cross-cutting
| ID | User story | Acceptance criteria |
|----|------------|---------------------|
| X-01 | As a user, I want **push notifications** when I am not in the app. | FCM/APNs; tap opens relevant thread; respects mute/block where applicable. |
| X-02 | As a user, I want to sign in with **email/password** or **Google** or **Apple**. | Flows complete; session persists per security rules. |
| X-03 | As a user, I want last messages available **offline** for reading. | Cached thread readable offline for last synced window; send queues when offline if product allows. |

